Hello there!
So im having this issue for a few days now, scouted forums to find a sollution yet without any luck. So the issue is that almost in every game i get disconnected for a few minutes (~30sec-2min) several times, and is sometimes present durring champ select too. This never happens when i just surf the net only when playing lol. I even contacted my internet provider, they told me there is no problem with the service. Tried turning off peer to peer, yet the problem is still present some forums mentioned some nasty programs that screw up your bandwidth but non is installed. I have 50mbs internet.{{champion:32}} 
Cheers!
